es you make will appear in the converted video before you actually make the changes and CSS decryption. The latter enables the decoding of a copy protection so your converted videos can be played without issue on any mobile device.","What the software disappointingly doesn&#39;t offer is a watermark function. We looked for a watermark feature in every product we reviewed because it allows you to earmark or personalize any video you want to share or post online. The software also doesn&#39;t offer as many advanced video settings as our top-ranked products, such as the ability to change the video&#39;s frame rate. You can, however, change the video resolution and bit rate."]},"id":"7bf218b8-a675-4835-a7cf-adb0b50e83d0","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Customization"},"id":"e85248a1-ae5c-420e-9162-afe00ab17648","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["The software&#39;s title is a bit of a misnomer; although it is called Nidesoft DVD to MP4 Converter, the application can actually convert DVDs into an assortment of other multimedia formats. In addition to common formats such as MPEG, AVI and WMV, the software can also convert video to DivX, a codec that has become popular because it can compress large video files while retaining the original video quality.","As expected, the DVD to MP4 converter&#39;s preset devices – the devices listed under the software&#39;s output profiles – include the ubiquitous iPod and iPhone, as well as many BlackBerry models and popular gaming consoles. What we liked and found rather surprising was that it also includes lesser-known (and in some cases borderline obscure) devices such as the Archos and Creative Zen MP3 players."]},"id":"a3b9d788-00d6-455e-a204-6e98923f8454","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Help &amp; Support"},"id":"8dc6f678-eb57-4c52-a2f5-b8eb4d778a3b","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["For all but the most inexperienced computer users, the Nidesoft DVD to MP4 Converter is simple to use. Its interface fosters intuitive n